* =============================================================================
* N2 EFFE validation — Run B phase 1
* CAS(6,6) / cc-pVDZ / 8 singlet roots / NoSym
* CASPT2: ONLY=1 ... ONLY=8  →  8 sequential per-root CASPT2 blocks
*
* Each block computes root N's row of H_eff (couplings to all other roots).
* JobIph is saved after RASSCF and reused by all 8 CASPT2 blocks.
* assemble_effe.py parses the couplings from this log and writes input_B_effe.
* =============================================================================

&GATEWAY
  Coord= n2.xyz
  Basis= cc-pVDZ
  Group= NoSym

&SEWARD
  Cholesky
End of Input

&RASSCF
  Symmetry= 1
  Spin=     1
  CIROOT=   8 8 1
  nActEl=   6 0 0
  Inactive= 4
  Ras2=     6
  THRS=     1.0e-08 1.0e-04 1.0e-04
  Levshft=  0.5
  Iteration= 200 50
  CIMX=     200
  SDAV=     500
End of Input

>>COPY $Project.JobIph $CurrDir/rasscf_B.JobIph

* --- Root 1 ---
&CASPT2
  MAXITER=  300
  Frozen=   2
  Multistate= all
  Imaginary Shift= 0.25
  Only= 1
End of Input

* --- Root 2 ---
&CASPT2
  MAXITER=  300
  Frozen=   2
  Multistate= all
  Imaginary Shift= 0.25
  Only= 2
End of Input

